<h2>Adding Books</h2>
<p>
dslibris will find all XHTML files with extensions .xht or .xhtml that are in your media's /book directory. These books will show up in the book browser.
</p>

<h2>Library Controls</h2>

<ul>
<li>[DPAD] walks through the list.</li>
<li>[A] or [TAP] opens the selected book.</li>
<li>[B] or [SELECT] return to the currently open book.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Reading Controls</h2>

<ul>
<li>[A],[R],[DPAD] or [TAP] advances one page.</li>
<li>[B],[L],[DPAD] or [TAP] retreats one page.</li>
<li>[X] inverts text.</li>
<li>[Y] changes the screen brightness.</li>
<li>[SELECT] enters the library browser.</li>
</ul>

